Argument Type Default Description <code>keywords</code> list of strings required Search queries, e.g. <code>["StarRocks materialized view syntax"]</code> <code>max_results</code> int <code>5</code> Maximum results to return (1–20) <code>include_domains</code> list of strings none Restrict results to specific domains, e.g. <code>["docs.snowflake.com"]</code> <p>Result:</p> <pre><code>{
  "query": "StarRocks materialized view syntax",
  "result_count": 5,
  "results": [
    {"title": "...", "url": "...", "snippet": "...", "age": "..."}
  ]
}
</code></pre>

参数 类型 默认值 说明 <code>keywords</code> 字符串列表 必填 搜索关键词，如 <code>["StarRocks materialized view syntax"]</code> <code>max_results</code> int <code>5</code> 返回结果数上限（1–20） <code>include_domains</code> 字符串列表 无 限定结果域名，如 <code>["docs.snowflake.com"]</code> <p>返回结果：</p> <pre><code>{
  "query": "StarRocks materialized view syntax",
  "result_count": 5,
  "results": [
    {"title": "...", "url": "...", "snippet": "...", "age": "..."}
  ]
}
</code></pre>
